        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8415",
        "content": "As it was, she pressed the picture to her bosom as she wondered if, perchance, he would not some day come out of his hiding to meet her.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
