        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8415",
        "content": "This was the formal beginning of her sense of personal companionship in the picture-companionship, yes, of delight in it, for there is even delight in tears-in some situations in life.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
