        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8415",
        "content": "Especially is this true of one whose emotions are her only guides, as seems to have been the case with the Widow Morris.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
