        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8415",
        "content": "Now, that hotel, when it was consumed by fire, which to it was the same as mortal death, why, it either ascended into Heaven, in smoke, or it fell, in ashes-to the other place.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
