        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8415",
        "content": "\"You know a man'll get tired of himself, even, if he's condemned to it too continual, and think of that blondinetted typewriter for a steady diet-to a man like Morris!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
