        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8415",
        "content": "Her neighbors understood that it must have been a shock \"to be suddenly confronted with any souvenir of the hotel fire\"--so one had expressed it-and the incident soon passed out of the village mind.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
